title: Great Condo in Boca! WOW! MUST SEE!
posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Fabulous updated, very spacious 2/2 with bonus room located in Whitehall Condo at Camino Real community.', 'This unit features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances with tile floor in kitchen and hardwood floors in living area.', 'Recent updates include new laminate flooring in bedrooms, new vanities in bathrooms, new vertical blinds on the sliders to balconies which have accordion hurricane shutters.', 'This unit also features 2 balconies, a separate laundry room, plus a bonus room which can be used as an office.', 'The community offers 2 heated pools, 2 clubhouses with bathroom and kitchen facilities.', 'All ages welcome.', 'Cable & water included in rent.', 'Located just minutes to Town Center for great shopping and restaurants.', 'I-95 within close proximity.']
